isCreatingSomething

public boolean isCreatingSomething(java.lang.String name)
Returns whether or not the player is creating a jail or a cell.

If you want to check to see if they're just creating a jail then use isCreatingAJail or if you want to see if they're creating a cell then use isCreatingACell.

Parameters:
name - The name of the player, in any case as we convert it to lowercase.
Returns:
True if the player is creating a jail or cell, false if they're not creating anything.
